opendial.bn.values

Interface Value

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Value>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ArrayVal, BooleanVal, DoubleVal, Effect, NoneVal, SetVal, StringVal

    public interface Value
extends java.lang.Comparable<Value>
    Generic interface for a variable value, that can be copied.

    The classes implementing this interface should also implement the hashcode(), equals() and toString() methods
